@@ -0,0 +1,15 @@
+#!/bin/bash
+## @test
+## @run shell CriuVersionTest.sh
+
+exec 2>&1
+set -x
+export
+whereis criu
+criu --version
+whoami
+sudo -n whoami
+find . -type f -iname criu /home/runner/jdk-linux-x64
+find . -type f -iname criu /home/runner/work/
+
+exit 1; # print output to log
\ No newline at end of file
